[{"id":"VR802588","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows an x y plane with a wire along the y axis. A small segment of wire on the positive y axis is shaded and is labeled l. A point P is on the positive x axis. The distance from the shaded wire segment to Point P is r.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR802588.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A long wire carries a current <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I\"><math alttext=\"I\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>I</mi></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></math></span></span> is located a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r\"><math alttext=\"r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>r</mi></math></span></span> from a small segment of the wire of length <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"l\"><math alttext=\"l\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mo>ℓ</mo></math></span></span>. The Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></math></span></span> on the positive <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span>-axis is a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span> from the origin. What is the magnitude of the magnetic field at Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>P</mtext></math></span></span> due to this wire segment alone?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR80